name: Erick Ludwick
description: I am a person who is positive about every aspect of life. There are many things I like to do and to experience. I like to dream, talk, and to listen. I like to see the sunrise in the morning and the moonlight at night I love delicious food and comfortable shoes. I’m very skittish bout love, but I’m ready to try again. My son means the world to me ,what I’m asking for is love, honestly and respect. I dislike lies but most of all I love hugs and kisses and a good laugh
